				\begin{document}${\sim} 40\,d_{i} \approx 0.3\,R_{\mathrm{E}}$\end{document}∼40di≈0.3RE, and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}${\sim}300\,d_{i} \approx 2.4\,R_{\mathrm{E}}$\end{document}∼300di≈2.4RE, respectively, where \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
